{"type": "article", "id": 23276, "title": "Normann Copenhagen 晾衣杆", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-04T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110758XpVtlEIdum0yRGYe.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是北欧家具品牌 Normann Copenhagen 联合设计师 Simon Legald 推出的晾衣杆。用橡木条做结构搭建出三角空间，上面是挂衣服铁杆，下面连接了带孔的平台，可以放上包和鞋帽。晾衣杆在设计上没有多余的部分，简洁干净，能适应任何环境。有黑白两种选择，大小型号分别宽 74cm、120cm ，售价 374 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/products/toj-clothes-rack-small?v=600015\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110756ptyQAI1aeri7fDM8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110756xSw2J7OYZWltIbFG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110757b5PJEVTH1jZYyofp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110757oqJ9QMr0yWc3si8A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110758kwYExP3KuXzyV6of.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}